617
00:36:49,230 --> 00:36:52,419
Tell me! Why are there illegal copper coins with Qian Printing?

618
00:36:52,419 --> 00:36:55,699
Qian Printing...? Illegal copper coins?

619
00:36:55,699 --> 00:36:58,060
I... I don't know.

